### 保存任务
POST http://127.0.0.1:10010/task
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uuid": "task1",
  "exec_file": "/bin/sh",
  "args": "-c /home/lifetime/timer/test.sh",
  "loop": true,
  "enable": false,
  "cron": "* * * * *"
}

### 获取任务列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:10010/task

### 获取任务详情
GET http://127.0.0.1:10010/task
  ?uuid=task1

### 删除任务
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:10010/task
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uuid": "task1"
}


### 运行任务
POST http://127.0.0.1:10010/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uuid": "task1"
}
